// Labour Law (views/law/labour.pug)
extends ../layouts/main

block content
  .law-container
    .container
      h1 Labour Law
      .law-section
        h2 Step 1: What is Labour Law about?
        p Labour law governs the relationship between employers, employees, and trade unions. In India, it is covered by numerous central and state laws dealing with industrial relations, working conditions, social security, and employment standards.
        p This area of law ensures fair treatment of workers, safe working conditions, and proper compensation while balancing employer interests and business operations.
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 2: Why do we need Labour Law and Solutions?
        h3 Why We Need Labour Law:
        ul
          li Protection of worker rights and safety
          li Fair wages and working conditions
          li Social security and benefits
          li Industrial harmony and dispute resolution
          li Prevention of exploitation
        h3 Solutions:
        ul
          li Compliance with labour laws and regulations
          li Proper employment contracts and policies
          li Regular safety audits and training
          li Dispute resolution mechanisms
          li Social security and benefits management
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 3: Help and Description
        h3 Key Areas of Labour Law:
        .labour-areas
          .area-card
            h4 Labour Law Filing
            p Compliance with various labour laws and returns
          .area-card
            h4 Mandatory Requirements
            p Statutory compliance and reporting obligations
          .area-card
            h4 Payroll Services
            p Salary processing and statutory deductions
          .area-card
            h4 Representation Services
            p Legal support in labour disputes
          .area-card
            h4 Due Diligence Services
            p Labour law compliance audits
        h3 Important Acts:
        ul
          li Industrial Disputes Act, 1947
          li Factories Act, 1948
          li Minimum Wages Act, 1948
          li Payment of Gratuity Act, 1972
          li Employees' Provident Funds Act, 1952
          li Shops and Commercial Establishments Act (State-specific)
      
      .chatbot-section
        h2 Labour Law Chatbot
        .chatbot-container
          .chat-messages#chat-messages
            .message.bot-message
              p Welcome! I can help you with labour law queries. What would you like to know about compliance, payroll, or employee rights?
          .chat-input-container
            input(type='text', id='chat-input', placeholder='Ask about labour law...', class='law-chat-input')
            button#send-btn Send